        pydockerfile
        ============
        
        ``pydockerfile`` gives simplistic Dockerfile parsing. It performs no validation.
        
        
        Installation
        ------------
        
        .. code-block:: bash
        
            pip install pydockerfile
        
        Usage
        -----
        
        .. code-block:: python
        
            import pydockerfile
            dockerfile = pydockerfile.parse_file('/path/to/Dockerfile')
            assert dockerfile.FROM
        
